title: The Returned S1 Ep5 - Serge Et Toni
description:
The Returned S1 Ep5 - Serge Et Toni

Serge Et Toni - The dead gradually come out into the open but are unable to resume normal lives. Camille is rejected by Frederick, and Simon is abruptly separated from Adele and Chloe when Thomas shoots at him, in self-defense. Victor wanders around, looking for his murderer. Julie begins to have doubts: what if she was dead too? Lena is treated by the serial killer as he strives to keep his murderous impulses under control. 

From France, in French
